{"tid":596854,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG谷] 孤兒瘋人院","createTime":"2018-03-18T05:35:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T17:38:47.000Z","uid":171592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f3cf2e0925cada43a87c08787aaead66e34e6799","tid":596854,"uid":171592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T05:35:23.000Z","msg":"孤兒瘋人院  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n專收集一堆說話太瘋癲而被踢的孤兒，隨意傾談你既所思所想，但以下人士請勿內進 <br />\n- 23歲以下人士  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n- 搵食人士即踢  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n- 狗公麻煩走啦  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n- 娘娘行遠啲呀  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地谷內已有專屬狗公、娘娘、搵食人士，佢地會不斷監察，以防有人威脅到佢地既地位。 <br />\n每個月會清一次深潛人士，拒絕cdrom，大家有心想傾計先入，谷內有來自各行各業既人，想傾乜都可以，只怕你開唔到題。  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/DzuS7EnAjDZj0wyN-zIbdg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDzuS7EnAjDZj0wyN-zIbdg&d=iZYmbYB9RV8p5MHDbqQo6v%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=98f33032\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/DzuS7EnAjDZj0wyN-zIbdg</a>"},{"pid":"71940f373316996f9f0c5a3e0925446544987a60","tid":596854,"uid":171592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T11:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7573c63e6d2a12dfdd42657605aa4888ffc1c74","tid":596854,"uid":171592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T14:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c36a37e112e8e1602c84698d940047c281d37f0","tid":596854,"uid":79233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T17:38:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">想請問版主, 若被 Bam! 後既朋友能否有機會請版主作 Un-bam 呢?<br />\n<br />\n同時:<br />\n<br />\n1: 原想像 HKG 內的 PM [留言] 直接給版主, 但後來先發覺原來兩個 Forum 有咁樣既差別。<br />\n2: 假如版主方便的話, 可以留 TG 內的 User ID (稱謂) 作聯絡呢? 望版大能回覆在下問題, 謝謝!</span>"}]}